<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Alert</title>
    <style>
        /* Your CSS styles for the email alert */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-alert {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .email-alert-content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .email-alert h2 {
            color: #ff5722;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-alert p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .mail-icon:before {
            content: "\2709"; /* Unicode for mail icon */
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .company-details {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }

        /* Highlighting styles */
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px; /* Increased size */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-alert">
        <div class="email-alert-content">
            <h2>Task Approval Request</h2>
            <p class="attention"><span class="mail-icon" style="font-size: 24px;">&#x2709;</span><strong>Attention:</strong> A task approval request has been received for the task <span id="task-name" class="highlight"><%= Task %></span>. The frequency for this task is <span id="task-frequency" class="highlight"><%= Frequency %></span> for the month of <%= Month %>, and the responsibility is as follows: <span id="task-responsibility" class="highlight"><%= Responsibility %></span>. Check the Dashboard for further details.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
